-G0pbrW1w","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"127","text":"Factores de riesgo","guid":"nUxh_GuU_zE3gQTHZY2eIA","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"FR para ITS","guid":"v2j7JC65NQ_ulCajQ9GA0w","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"139","text":"FR para enf. transmitidas por sangre","guid":"5qGrMi6FTPF2V-99st69Hg","children":[]}]},{"id":"142","parent":"127","text":"Nota: Linfadenopatía ≥12 meses sin cambios tamaño/síntomas sistémicos → Sugiere causa no maligna","guid":"CrJLc75pSMhbtocQl6jG4w","children":[]}]},{"id":"143","parent":"126","text":"Examen Físico\\NFocalizado","guid":"tX8YfZ5U97PZv8-Ii4sHbA","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"Examinar ganglios en cada región drenaje","guid":"_bbFCXVnNUcBmx8nPT0Hhw","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"143","text":"Buscar signos enf. sistémica (esplenomegalia, hepatomegalia)","guid":"tJj55e3c5Rss4uuZXytRyw","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"143","text":"Identificar procesos inflamatorios locales (amigdalitis viral)","guid":"qBL4XZtfIwJpq_MZBMMGyQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"147","parent":"126","text":"Examen\\NGanglionar","guid":"oUMMobgl_xX17WcAs-CQww","children":[{"id":"148","parent":"147","text":"Palpación\\NGanglionar","guid":"xmEbMhnfLVpZPb1y8sryUQ","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"Instrucciones: Paciente relaja área a examinar","guid":"uglxTl4nvLeSmbx0KEPskA","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"148","text":"Palpar suavemente con yemas dedos","guid":"P2M4NEqxHqRBidH1E5as8A","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"148","text":"Evaluar: Tamaño, consistencia, sensibilidad, fijación","guid":"W3AulF5nv9KtMbOQiOEiPA","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"148","text":"Buscar: Signos alarma causa metastásica","guid":"9KGGWgMGWhgBjZbK6egj6Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"153","parent":"147","text":"Palpación Ganglios\\NCabeza y Cuello","guid":"twWM8FbOREp6WKlowEcimw","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"Instrucciones: Cuello relajado, ligeramente flexionado","guid":"vgQRP1uqCGmOMZVUMZpC1w","